sequenceDiagram
    participant Config
    participant API
    participant CParser as Dedicated Container Parser
    participant EParser as Dedicated Element Parser
    participant Batch
    participant Env
    participant Handoff

    Config->>Config: Resolve container shape + container parser + element parser
    API->>CParser: MT5 array/container
    loop each element
        CParser->>EParser: parse known element type
        EParser-->>CParser: parsed element result
    end
    CParser-->>Batch: Parsed batch ref
    Batch-->>Env: Batch-as-single or element-stream strategy (descriptor)
    Env->>Handoff: Later handoff contract
